*** Appel =E0 communications ***

Des EIAH centr=E9s apprenants pour l'apprentissage tout au long de la vie (=
ATLV)

http://recherche.telecom-bretagne.eu/atlv/

Conf=E9rence Environnements Informatiques pour l'Apprentissage Humain (EIAH=
 2017<http://eiah2017.unistra.fr/>)

6 au 9 juin 2017, Strasbourg, France



=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=
=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=
