<ul>
<li><span style=3D"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif;=
" data-mce-style=3D"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif=
;">Quels dispositifs renforcent le pouvoir d=92agir de la personne et favor=
isent la prise de conscience ?</span>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif;=
" data-mce-style=3D"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif=
;">En mettant les apprenants en situation de r=E9ussite</span></li><li><spa=
n style=3D"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif;" data-m=
